-- Lend Lease Seeks $267 Million Capital Raising for Fund, Australian Says
-- Nichola Saminather
-- 2010-07-28T21:28:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/lend-lease-seeks-267-million-capital-raising-for-fund-australian-says.html

          
          
             Lend Lease Group will raise A$300
million for its unlisted wholesale office fund to repay debt and
make acquisitions in a recovering market, the Australian
newspaper reported citing Chief Investment Officer Rob
Hattersley. Existing investors are expected to take up more than
half of the offering, the report said.  
